## On Case Updated Request Mapping Template
## VTL template for onCaseUpdated subscription

{
  "version": "2017-02-28",
  "operation": "UpdateItem",
  "key": {
    "id": $util.dynamodb.toDynamoDBJson($context.source.id)
  },
  "update": {
    "expression": "SET #updatedAt = :updatedAt",
    "expressionNames": {
      "#updatedAt": "updatedAt"
    },
    "expressionValues": {
      ":updatedAt": $util.dynamodb.toDynamoDBJson($util.time.nowISO8601())
    }
  }
}
